data.description: Opportunity knocks: Back on the market fell out of escrow as buyer did not perform. [Buyer interest rate buy-down OR closing cost incentive up to 2% with a full price offer!] A stunning & quality home, as new without the wait! The soaring foyer entry leads you to the great room with a cozy gas fireplace and an inviting atmosphere. The adjoining kitchen is a chef's dream featuring a large island, convenient breakfast bar & dining area. MAIN FLOOR OFFICE | BEDROOM. The large primary suite features dual vanities, a walk-in shower & a generous walk-in closet. Upstairs there are 4 additional bedrooms with substantial closets + you'll also find the utility room providing added convenience & storage! Step out back and relax in the fully fenced backyard & covered outdoor patio. The three bay tandem garage has space for all your toys. The community amenities include a swimming pool, walking trails, fiber optic internet & community green spaces. [FIND THE BEST KEPT SECRET IN THE BOISE METRO AREA!]
